好<br />\n當你營養唔夠嗰陣你食幾多都會肚餓<br />\nfocus喺蛋肉類海鮮蔬菜呢啲營養密度高嘅食物先啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"唔會齋食掛<br />\n加多隻蛋或者雞胸肉 加多幾條菜<br />\n都己經有唔錯既營養"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:56:11.000Z","msg":"得隻蛋有啲營養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得罪講句雞胸係肉類入面算營養價值最差嗰隻<br />\n雞髀或者紅肉無論係營養或者口感都完勝雞胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T09:37:12.000Z","msg":"唔識咪亂up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd0d9c9a57eab708c7e341ab4a82fa6baf0e93b","tid":2203133,"uid":266282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T09:37:54.000Z","msg":"問下肥媽<br />\n佢教人減肥"},{"pid":"87bbd6de7c1d7c86f2c712eec6e6fc40ed608748","tid":2203133,"uid":270308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"你食嗰吓好頂肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但之後好快就餓返"},{"pid":"e20e9d85f4b5511c5c937a0468cf22ae6e7359e5","tid":2203133,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"98bfda5ad0b6a64ceec8f1ef113b806bd679bf85","tid":2203133,"uid":18899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feea682ab8a50a9cd05692c859e5c5b7d97cab7b","tid":2203133,"uid":198389,"like":1,"dislike":38,"score":-37,"quote":{"pid":"29eb34b744e9130c6cb0ce9d0bd84893fb27d2fb","tid":2203133,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"唔會齋食掛<br />\n加多隻蛋或者雞胸肉 加多幾條菜<br />\n都己經有唔錯既營養"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:56:11.000Z","msg":"得隻蛋有啲營養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得罪講句雞胸係肉類入面算營養價值最差嗰隻<br />\n雞髀或者紅肉無論係營養或者口感都完勝雞胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T09:37:12.000Z","msg":"唔識咪亂up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:20:37.000Z","msg":"上面有咩錯歡迎指正 